────────────────────────────────────────────
📦 FILE ORGANIZER PRO
────────────────────────────────────────────

🧹 Automatically organizes your files by type and extension.
Save time and keep your folders clean and tidy in seconds!

────────────────────────────────────────────
⚙️ HOW TO USE
────────────────────────────────────────────
1️⃣ Run the program (FileOrganizerPro.exe)
2️⃣ Select the folder you want to organize
3️⃣ Click "Organize Files"
4️⃣ Done! Files will be moved into subfolders like:
    - Documents
    - Images
    - Videos
    - Music
    - Others

Optional:
- Use the “Undo” button to restore files to their original locations.
- All changes are logged in “organizer_log.txt”.

────────────────────────────────────────────
✨ FEATURES
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ Clean, modern graphical interface (GUI)
✔ Automatic file classification by extension
✔ Undo and logging system
✔ Supports English and Spanish
✔ 100% offline – no internet required
✔ Compatible with Windows 10/11

────────────────────────────────────────────
💾 SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
────────────────────────────────────────────
• Windows 10 / 11
• No installation required (standalone EXE)
• Optional: Python 3.10+ (for script version)

